### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">أَلَمْ يَرَوْا۟ أَنَّا جَعَلْنَا ٱلَّيْلَ لِيَسْكُنُوا۟ فِيهِ وَٱلنَّهَارَ مُبْصِرًا ۚ إِنَّ فِى ذَٰلِكَ لَـَٔايَـٰتٍ لِّقَوْمٍ يُؤْمِنُونَ</span>

### English

Do they not see that We made the night for them to rest in and the day bright? Surely in this are signs for those who believe.